@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false

title Sequence Diagram: Driver Registration and Verification

actor Driver
participant System
participant Administrator

Driver -> System: Register (Profile, Vehicle Details)
Driver -> System: Upload Documents (License, Registration)
System --> Administrator: Notify New Driver Registration
Administrator -> System: Login
Administrator -> System: View Driver Accounts/Documents
Administrator -> System: Verify Documents
alt Valid Documents
System --> Driver: Account Approved/Activated
else Invalid
System --> Driver: Rejection Notification
Driver -> System: Revise/Upload New Documents
end
@enduml
